fields.description:
I would like to be able to use IQL placeholders to get data from JSM fields that are objects (rather than just plain text fields), for example, the Customer Request Type field is an object, and to get the "Name" of the Customer Request Type, I would need to reference: {{requestType.name}}

I would use this in the *Filter Assign Scope (IQL)* field in the custom field setup, using a placeholder like: Name = ${requestType.name}

 

This is a continuation request from this one: JSDSERVER-7425: Placeholder for Service Desk request types
